OL,3,CThe Ridings shopping centre to be
OL,4,Cdemolished after 43 years
OL,6,FWakefield's landmark shopping centre
OL,7,FThe Ridings is to be demolished to
OL,8,Fmake way for a housing and leisure
OL,9,Fdevelopment.
OL,11,FBuilt in 1983, the centre will be
OL,12,Fbulldozed to be replaced by a project,
OL,13,Fcalled Cathedral Quarter, including
OL,14,Fhomes and a cinema.
OL,16,FThe city council says the centre has
OL,17,Fstruggled for years because of online
OL,18,Fshopping and a decline in footfall.
OL,20,FThe announcement comes after both M&S
OL,21,Fand Primark pulled out.
