OL,3,CThe Ridings shopping centre to be
OL,4,Cdemolished after 43 years
OL,6,FCllr Jack Hemingway said: "We don't
OL,7,Funderestimate the strength of feeling
OL,8,Fabout The Ridings. It's been a huge
OL,9,Fpart of our city and once helped to
OL,10,Fput us on the map. But that is not the
OL,11,Fshopping centre you see now."
OL,13,FThe plan, to take 10 to 15 years,
OL,14,Fincludes more than 1,000 homes, green
OL,15,Fspaces, restaurants, a cinema and
OL,16,Fparking.
OL,18,FA new library and museum are also
OL,19,Fplanned.
