OL,3,CThe Ridings shopping centre to be
OL,4,Cdemolished after 43 years
OL,6,FThe council says businesses will be
OL,7,Fsupported if they want to stay in
OL,8,FWakefield.
OL,10,FNearby city apartment blocks,
OL,11,FGreenwood, Manor, Trinity, Tudor and
OL,12,FWarren House, are also being replaced
OL,13,Fwith about 200 "sustainable" homes.
OL,15,FThe plans will be considered at the
OL,16,Fcouncil's cabinet meeting on 17
OL,17,FFebruary.
OL,19,FIf approved, a consultation will then
OL,20,Fstart.
