OL,3,CThe Ridings shopping centre to be
OL,4,Cdemolished after 43 years
OL,6,FZahid Iqbal, owner of The Ridings,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Ridings has been a key part
OL,8,Fof the city for over 40 years. But now
OL,9,Fit is time for change.
OL,11,F"These plans are in the best interests
OL,12,Ffor the future of the city. And I
OL,13,Freally hope everyone gets behind these
OL,14,Fbold plans for Wakefield."
